<div class=3D"">The Connected Learning Initiative (CLIx) is an initiative o=
f the Tata Trusts in collaboration with the Tata Institute of Social Scienc=
es (TISS) and the Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT). Through mean=
ingful integration of technology into
 the high school curriculum CLIx aims to provide interactive, hands-on lear=
ning experiences in Mathematics, three Science subjects, Communicative Engl=
ish, as well as digital literacy, blended with value education for students=
 and for teacher professional development.</div>
<div class=3D""><br class=3D"">
</div>
<div class=3D"">Internship/fellowship applications are invited in the area =
of Education Technology for Curriculum production and Development of digita=
l interactive tools like simulation and games and development for OpenEdX. =
Proficiency in HTML5/CSS3, JavaScript,
 Python/Django and Linux, interest in edu- cation, good communication skill=
s and ability to work on time bound projects are desirable.</div>
<div class=3D""><br class=3D"">
</div>
<div class=3D"">Duration: 6 months to 1 year including (mentoring by MIT). =
Stipend: Starting Rs 30,000 pm (based on experience, and salary protection =
if relevant); expenses for travel and stay at MIT and on the field. Fresh g=
raduates as well as employed professionals
 or faculty are welcome to apply. <b class=3D"">The last date for receiving=
